videos.description: UConn's Kia Nurse finds Saniya Chong open in the left wing, Chong catches and shoots to give the Huskies an early 13-7 lead.
videos.headline: Chong drains a three early on for UConn

videos.description: UConn's Gabby Williams hops into the passing lane to come away with a steal, then lays it in on the other end.
videos.headline: Williams slashes in for the steal then lays it in

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson draws contact but is still able to lay it in.
videos.headline: Samuelson catches in transition then scores plus the foul

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson comes around a screen, catches a pass then knocks down a jumper.
videos.headline: Samuelson connects on catch and shoot jumper

videos.description: Crystal Dangerfield finds Napheesa Collier on a great no look pass.
videos.headline: Fantastic no look pass from Dangerfield sets up a UConn scoer
